Class KeywordTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • aims.photo.uploader.tablemodels.KeywordTree

  • public class KeywordTree
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by IntelliJ IDEA. User: gcoleman Date: 16/01/2008 Time: 11:35:20 Last Updated: 14/12/2012 By: Timothy Hart A KeywordTree class is used to build the keyword tree structure for use in the GUI. It calls upon the KeywordLookup, LocationLookup and TaxaLookup classes to retrieve the data required. Using that data it builds a tree structure using both DefualtMutableTreeNode and SortableTreeNode objects.

    Timothy Hart
